Run the `curl` command to confirm that your web page is available.

```bash
# ~/chef-repo
$ curl localhost
<html>
  <body>
    <h1>hello world</h1>
  </body>
</html>
```

Optionally, from a web browser on another machine, navigate to your server. You'll see something like this.

